text: Yousra Abdel Razek (born December 3, 1995, also known as Yousra Helmy) is an Egyptian table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics as part of the Egyptian team in the women's team event. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Egypt Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Competitors at the 2019 African Games Category:African Games gold medalists for Egypt Category:African Games bronze medalists for Egypt Category:African Games medalists in table tennis Category:African Games competitors for Egypt
